{"id":789,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":789,"title":"Jeremiah 20","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 20"],[".studySummary",["i","Jeremiah is smitten and put in the stocks—He prophesies that all Judah will be taken captive by Babylon."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.1","order":"02.25.020.52159"},["b","1"],"Now",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Pashur"],"the son of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Immer"],"the priest, who",["i","was"],"also",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"chief governor"],"in the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", heard that Jeremiah prophesied these things."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.2","order":"02.25.020.52160"},["b","2"],"Then Pashur",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"smote"],"Jeremiah the prophet, and put him in the stocks that",["i","were"],"in the high gate of Benjamin, which",["i","was"],"by the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.3","order":"02.25.020.52161"},["b","3"],"And it came to pass on the morrow, that Pashur brought forth Jeremiah out of the stocks. Then said Jeremiah unto him, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath not called thy name Pashur, but",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Magor-missabib"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.4","order":"02.25.020.52162"},["b","4"],"For thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", Behold, I will make thee a terror to thyself, and to all thy friends: and they shall fall by the sword of their enemies, and thine eyes shall behold",["i","it:"],"and I will give all Judah into the hand of the king of Babylon, and he shall carry them",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"captive"],"into Babylon, and shall slay them with the sword."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.5","order":"02.25.020.52163"},["b","5"],"Moreover I will deliver all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"strength"],"of this city, and all the labours thereof, and all the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"precious"],"things thereof, and all the treasures of the kings of Judah will I give into the hand of their enemies, which shall spoil them, and take them, and carry them to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"Babylon"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.6","order":"02.25.020.52164"},["b","6"],"And thou, Pashur, and all that dwell in thine house shall go into captivity: and thou shalt come to Babylon, and there thou shalt die, and shalt be buried there, thou, and all thy friends, to whom thou hast prophesied",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"lies"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.7","order":"02.25.020.52165"},["b","7"],"¶O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", thou hast",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"deceived"],"me, and I was deceived: thou art stronger than I, and hast prevailed: I am in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"derision"],"daily, every one mocketh me."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.8","order":"02.25.020.52166"},["b","8"],"For since I spake, I cried out, I cried",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"violence"],"and spoil; because the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was made a reproach unto me, and a derision, daily."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.9","order":"02.25.020.52167"},["b","9"],"Then I said, I will not make mention of him, nor speak any more in his name. But",["i","his word"],"was in mine heart as a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"burning"],"fire shut up in my bones, and I was weary with forbearing, and I could not",["i",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"stay"],"."]],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.10","order":"02.25.020.52168"},["b","10"],"¶For I heard the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"defaming"],"of many, fear on every side. Report,",["i","say they,"],"and we will report it. All my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"familiars"],"watched for my halting,",["i","saying,"],"Peradventure he will be enticed, and we shall prevail against him, and we shall take our revenge on him."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.11","order":"02.25.020.52169"},["b","11"],"But the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"with me as a mighty terrible one: therefore my persecutors shall stumble, and they shall not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"prevail"],": they shall be greatly ashamed; for they shall not prosper:",["i","their"],"everlasting",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"confusion"],"shall never be forgotten."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.12","order":"02.25.020.52170"},["b","12"],"But, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"triest"],"the righteous,",["i","and"],"seest the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"reins"],"and the heart, let me see thy vengeance on them: for unto thee have I opened my cause."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.13","order":"02.25.020.52171"},["b","13"],"Sing unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", praise ye the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": for he hath delivered the soul of the poor from the hand of evildoers."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.14","order":"02.25.020.52172"},["b","14"],"¶",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Cursed"],["i","be"],"the day wherein I was born: let not the day wherein my mother bare me be blessed."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.15","order":"02.25.020.52173"},["b","15"],"Cursed",["i","be"],"the man who brought tidings to my father, saying, A man child is born unto thee; making him very glad."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.16","order":"02.25.020.52174"},["b","16"],"And let that man be as the cities which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"overthrew"],", and repented not: and let him hear the cry in the morning, and the shouting at noontide;"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.17","order":"02.25.020.52175"},["b","17"],"Because he slew me not from the womb; or that my mother might have been my grave, and her womb",["i","to be"],"always great",["i","with me."]],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.18","order":"02.25.020.52176"},["b","18"],"Wherefore came I forth out of the womb to see labour and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"sorrow"],", that my days should be consumed with shame?"]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.1a","order":"02.25.020.52177"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/21.1"},"Jer. 21:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/38.1"},"38:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.1b","order":"02.25.020.52179"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/24.14"},"1 Chr. 24:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.1c","order":"02.25.020.52181"},["b","1c"],["span.small","OR"],"senior officer."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.2a","order":"02.25.020.52183"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/16.2"},"1 Ne. 16:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.24.24-27"},"Hel. 13:24 (24–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.3a","order":"02.25.020.52185"},["b","3a"],["span.small","IE"],"Terror all around."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.4a","order":"02.25.020.52187"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1.13.11-14"},"1 Ne. 1:13 (11–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.5a","order":"02.25.020.52189"},["b","5a"],["span.small","HEB"],"provision or goods."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.5b","order":"02.25.020.52191"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.25"},"Ezek. 22:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.5c","order":"02.25.020.52193"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/24.12.12-16"},"2 Kgs. 24:12 (12–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/25.13.13-17"},"25:13 (13–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.6a","order":"02.25.020.52195"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lying"},"TG Lying"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.7a","order":"02.25.020.52197"},["b","7a"],["span.small","HEB"],"persuaded."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.7b","order":"02.25.020.52199"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/3.14"},"Lam. 3:14"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/despair"},"TG Despair"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/suffering"},"Suffering"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.8a","order":"02.25.020.52201"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.7"},"Jer. 6:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.9a","order":"02.25.020.52203"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.3"},"Ps. 39:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.3"},"3 Ne. 11:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.9b","order":"02.25.020.52205"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.20"},"Acts 4:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/12.2"},"Ether 12:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.10a","order":"02.25.020.52207"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/31.13"},"Ps. 31:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.10b","order":"02.25.020.52209"},["b","10b"],["span.small","OR"],"familiar friends."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.11a","order":"02.25.020.52211"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/protection-divine"},"TG Protection, Divine"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.11b","order":"02.25.020.52213"},["b","11b"],["span.small","OR"],"disgrace."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.12a","order":"02.25.020.52215"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"TG Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.12b","order":"02.25.020.52217"},["b","12b"],["span.small","HEB"],"inward parts."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.14a","order":"02.25.020.52219"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/3.3.3-4"},"Job 3:3 (3–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.16a","order":"02.25.020.52221"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/13.19.19-20"},"Isa. 13:19 (19–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.18a","order":"02.25.020.52223"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sorrow"},"TG Sorrow"],"."]]}
